title: How many songs have Honey Singh written to date? - Quora

response.answer_text: There is no offical record of how many Songs Honey singh has written because in the industry especially in bollywood credits are not given properly.Honey singh Has co written songs with many artists like Badshah,Raftaar and Lil golu.Nowadays H singh co writes along with Lil golu.His album International Villagers has many writers.And He has co written Desi Kalakar with Lil Golu
